entries.title: Beyoncé Wins Zero People's Choice Country Awards Despite 17 Nominations

entries.title: Prince Harry will visit Lesotho for first time in six years to support his first charity Sentebale - with no mention of whether Meghan will be joining him
entries.summary: The Duke of Sussex will travel to Lesotho early next month for a gathering of business leaders, philanthropists and local stakeholders, aimed at driving forward the work of his charity Sentebale.
